                    <summary type="html">
                        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.alexbolboaca.ro/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/Global-Day-of-Code-Retreat_v2.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;alignleft size-medium wp-image-653&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; src=&quot;http://www.alexbolboaca.ro/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/Global-Day-of-Code-Retreat_v2-212x300.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Global Day of Code Retreat&quot; width=&quot;212&quot;&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
